sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Cron as Mesin Penjadwal
    participant Sistem
    participant Basis Data
    participant Chatbot

    Cron->>Sistem: Trigger jadwal harian
    Sistem->>Basis Data: Cari tagihan jatuh tempo
    Basis Data-->>Sistem: List tagihan
    
    loop Per Tagihan
        Sistem->>Basis Data: Catat log notifikasi
        Sistem->>Chatbot: Kirim pesan WA/Push
        Chatbot-->>Sistem: Respons terkirim
    end